data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with a 2 car garage that features a bonus loft and bonus room/office on the 1st floor! This 2 story home has tile floors throughout the main living areas, espresso wood cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. All bedrooms are located upstairs and have generous walk-in closets. Enjoy the spacious back and side yard of this over-sized homesite with a newly installed privacy fence to encompass the backyard! Don't miss this opportunity to own your own little piece of paradise. Schedule your showing today!
